{"type": "article", "id": 12170, "title": "桌椅组合", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-16T10:29:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607185150NCYxztV6LkydcEIK.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款桌椅组合，桌子名为 Donald，椅子名为 Little Sidekicks，它们的设计灵感来自折叠的纸张，看起来像椅子一样灵活易折叠，但又有着木材的质感。设计师把几层木制薄板结合在一起，采用层压弯曲技术使其成型，等待胶水干透后木材之间的结合更加无缝美观。凳子腿部有一个开叉的设计，中间的部分重叠让凳子更加坚固。\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140002tsRNqniDScW83Evw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140003Lbgp4nS0MqWoJQOK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140003R2YP6JHwyp75Abf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140004AJFLc913QOhEvXfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261400048HKv1pVd49LOaAfW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}